ALL SYMBOLS PAY FROM LEFT TO RIGHT. BONUS PAYS ON ANY POSITION.
All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher

All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines.
All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
Bonus wins are multiplied by total bet.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Only the highest win is paid per line.
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.

The Jackpot amounts go up basedon contributions taken from all participating player bets, as follows:
- {0} from each bet goes into GRAND Jackpot
- {0} from each bet goes into MEGA Jackpot
- {0} from each bet goes into MAJOR Jackpot
- {0} from each bet goes into MINOR Jackpot
Expected individual contributions to the Jackpot can vary due to currency conversion and rounding at the third decimal.
The Jackpots can be won at random at the end of any spin in the base game. Jackpots cannot be won during the FREE SPINS or MONEY RESPIN feature.
The winning JACKPOT is revealed by opening items in a bonus screen until you reveal 3 with the same name.

A player’s chance to win any of the available progressive Jackpots is directly related to the bet amount. Higher bets have a higher chance of winning. However, any of the Jackpots can be won with any bet 
amount above the minimum eligible bet.
When any of the Jackpots is won, it will be reseeded with an amount set aside for this purpose from each participating contributions and start again to build from that seed.

Funds for next seed are gathered from a part of the contributions taken from all bets. The funds gathered are put on the side and will be used to fund the Jackpot after being won. Contributions for future seeds are as follows:
- {0} from each contribution is set aside for the next seed of GRAND Jackpot.
- {0} from each contribution is set aside for the next seed of MEGA Jackpot.
- {0} from each contribution is set aside for the next seed of MAJOR Jackpot.
- {0} from each contribution is set aside for the next seed of MINOR Jackpot.
Due to unavoidable internet lag, the displayed Jackpot amounts may differ from actual values.

If two or more players win the Jackpot at approximately the same time, then all wins are awarded in order, so that each collects the accumulated Jackpot value which exists at the exact moment of their win. The Jackpot is not divided equally among several winners.
Upon closure of an unpaid jackpot, player contributions will be transferred to another jackpot.

Jackpot may be temporarily shut down. When the jackpots are shut down, all contributions are stopped and the jackpots are marked as "Jackpot closed". The amount accumulated before shut down remains in the Jackpot and will be available for winning after the jackpots are resumed.
